name: A Song of Hex and Jynx - #1 A Witch Bows To No Man
description:
Introducing "A Song of Hex and Jynx", a series of three witch sisters, surviving and protecting each other.

This is the first story when one of the witch met a young lad, who broke her heart and almost killed the sisters. They joined hand to escape, after they made the man paid for what he did. They ran away together and in silence they enchanted their mother’s last words; ‘A Witch bows to no man’.
